<p>So basically when i print my array it looks like this:</p>  <pre><code>      P00       P01       P02             P10       P11       P12              P20       P21       P22  </code></pre>  <p>I want it to look like this: </p>  <pre><code>             M[0][0]   M[0][1]   M[0][2]          M[0][0] P00       P01       P02              M[1][0] P10       P11       P12             M[2][0] P20       P21       P22       </code></pre>  <p>My code:</p>  <pre><code> for (z=0; z&lt;N; z++){                for (c=0; c&lt;N;c++){                 printf("\t%p", &amp;M[z][c]);     }     printf("\n");           } </code></pre>  <p>Note that Pxx is the pointer address </p>